A yearly subscription is refundable within 14 days of purchase and includes a 365-day membership. Examinations that were due to be written by final-year pupils at the school were postponed a day earlier, Debbie Schaffer, the Education Minister in the Western Cape province, said in an emailed statement. The protest was the second to be staged at the school this month after reports emerged that invitations to a private gathering for its final-year students had mainly been extended to White pupils. The EFF, which has a predominantly Black membership and support base, has staged numerous protests over perceived racism — still a highly sensitive issue in the country more than a quarter-century after White-minority rule ended. © 2020 Bloomberg